      "front": "I am at home.",
      "back": "أنا في البيت.",
      "romanized": "ana fi al-bayt.",
      "grammarNote": "Pattern: Subject + في + Place (no verb 'to be' in present tense). أنا في البيت = 'I [am] in the house.' The equational sentence structure makes this very direct."
